            "code": "import numpy as np\nfrom scipy.optimize import fsolve\n\n# Define the equation\ndef equation(x):\n    return np.sin(x) + x**2 - 42\n\n# Let's guess some values to find possible solutions\ninitial_guesses = [6, -6]\n\n# Find roots\nroots = [fsolve(equation, guess)[0] for guess in initial_guesses]\nroots = np.array(roots)\n\nroots",
